* Installation

You can add this overlay through layman by:

layman -f -o http://github.com/downloads/monoid/gentoo-astronomy/astronomy-layman.xml -a astronomy

Better way is to add custom overlay list to overlays in
/etc/layman/layman.cfg: add

  https://raw.github.com/monoid/gentoo-astronomy/master/astronomy.xml

to `overlays` in /etc/layman/layman.cfg.  Then run

  layman -S -a astronomy


* Dependencies

Some packages of this overlay depends on packages in java-overlay:

layman -a java-overlay
